					<PARAFORMAT justify="center">(Added City Record 9/20/2023, eff. 10/20/2023) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-090]</HIGHLIGHTER>
