		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-141973" number="16260" version="2592">
								<HEADING>§ 8201-01 Referenced Standard Modifications and Amendments Thereto.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-1707" name="T03C082_8201-01"/>§ 8201-01 <CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Referenced Standard Modifications and Amendments Thereto.</CHARFORMAT>
								</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-141822" number="16261" version="2591">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Scope.</CHARFORMAT> This section sets forth provisions relating to the Department&apos;s adoption of modifications to the Referenced Standards set forth in <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="FC Chapter 45" destination-id="0-0-0-0">FC Chapter 45</LINK>, adoption of amendments to the Referenced Standard modifications codified in <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="FC Appendix B" destination-id="0-0-0-0">FC Appendix B</LINK>, and incorporation of such modifications and amendments into <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="FC Appendix B" destination-id="0-0-0-0">FC Appendix B</LINK>.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-141823" number="16262" version="2591">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">General Provisions.</CHARFORMAT>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-141824" number="16263" version="2591">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Adoption.</CHARFORMAT> The Referenced Standards set forth in <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="FC Chapter 45" destination-id="0-0-0-0">FC Chapter 45</LINK>, and the modifications thereto, as codified in <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="FC Appendix B" destination-id="0-0-0-0">FC Appendix B</LINK>, are amended as set forth in this chapter of the rules.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-141825" number="16264" version="2591">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Incorporation.</CHARFORMAT> Pursuant to FC 102.6.2, such Referenced Standard modifications and amendments to Referenced Standard modifications shall be deemed incorporated into <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="FC Appendix B" destination-id="0-0-0-0">FC Appendix B</LINK>.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-141826" number="16265" version="2591">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(3)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Identification of modifications and amendments.</CHARFORMAT>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-141827" number="16266" version="2591">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(A)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The text of the Referenced Standard modifications to be incorporated into <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="FC Appendix B" destination-id="0-0-0-0">FC Appendix B</LINK> is set forth in the respective sections of this chapter of the rules. The addition of such modifications to <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="FC Appendix B" destination-id="0-0-0-0">FC Appendix B</LINK> is indicated by underlining.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-141828" number="16267" version="2591">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(B)<TAB tab-count="1"/>When a Referenced Standard modification codified in <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="FC Appendix B" destination-id="0-0-0-0">FC Appendix B</LINK> is to be amended, the existing, codified text of the Referenced Standard modification is shown, with the language deleted in [brackets] and language added underlining.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-141966" number="16268" version="2591">
									<PARA>(Renumbered City Record 9/20/2023, eff. 10/20/2023) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-090]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
